title: 2016 Smart Vote USA - Clinton
description:
US Presidential Election Trump vs Clinton

In the US we usually vote democrat, republican or third party year after year. Have you ever wondered why? Do you really know what your political party currently stands for? 

Things change and so do party platforms. For instance, the old adage that democrats are the "blue collar" party may not necessarily represent your opinion about issues such as higher taxes, lack of school choice or excessive gun control.

"2016 Smart Vote USA" is a collection of various news clips, documentaries and other helpful election information packaged into an executable. The package includes reduced size videos suitable for mobile devices. The images are hyperlinked to larger sized videos on YouTube.
